Some schools in the region dealing with the fallout from high winds over the weekend have announced closings and delays for Monday. The following is a list of closings and delays: ●Fairfax County Public Schools will close the following seven schools that do not have power: Canterbury Woods Elementary, Crossfield Elementary, Forestville Elementary, Freedom Hill Elementary, Lynbrook Elementary, Parklawn Elementary, Westbriar Elementary. ● ●Fauquier County Public Schools will open 2 hours late. ●Prince William County Public Schools will open 2 hours late. ●Rappahannock County Public Schools will open 2 hours late. 